==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rehash
<hw>Re*hash"</hw> <pr>(r?*h?sh")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To hash
over again; to prepare or use again; <as>as, to <ex>rehash</ex> old
arguments</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rehash</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Rehash
<hw>Re*hash"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Something hashed over, or made up
from old materials.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rehear</ent>⟦br⟧
